OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cooler and more changeable
OL,6,Fday on Thursday, with a band of patchy
OL,7,Frain moving eastwards through the
OL,8,Fmorning. Clearing in the afternoon
OL,9,Fleaving sunny spells and blustery
OL,10,Fshowers, these most frequent across
OL,11,FCumbria.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA bright end to the afternoon
OL,14,Fwith a few showers lingering into the
OL,15,Fevening, however most places becoming
OL,16,Fdry overnight with cloudier skies
OL,17,Fdeveloping after midnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
