OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA dry start, but cloudy skies
OL,6,Falready across the south of the region
OL,7,Fwill continue to spread north with
OL,8,Foutbreaks of rain arriving during the
OL,9,Fafternoon. Becoming rather breezy
OL,10,Flater.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,13,FUnsettled through the weekend and
OL,14,FMonday with sunny spells and showers
OL,15,For longer spells of rain. The showers
OL,16,Flocally heavy with thunder. Windy with
OL,17,Fcoastal gales possible, temperatures
OL,18,Fnear average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
